sleMplsTpVplsCfgInfoTable.name: sleMplsTpVplsCfgInfoTable
sleMplsTpVplsCfgInfoTable.description: This table specifies information for configuring and status monitoring that is common to all service types and PSN types of VPLS.

sleMplsTpVplsCfgInfoEntry.description: A row in this table is indexed by sleMplsTpPwCfgNameInfo.

sleMplsTpVplsCfgInfoMacLearningLimit.description: MAC Learning Limit of the VPLS. 32767 is default mac learning limit.

sleMplsTpVplsCfgControlRequest.description: his object holds the possible read-write columns that can be modified in the sleMplsTpVplsCfg table. For each read-write column of sleMplsTpVplsCfg table, a Set Operation control value is added in this object.

sleMplsTpVplsCfgControlTimestamp.description: This object specifies the time at which the configuration is done.

sleMplsTpVplsCfgControlReqResult.description: The standard result of the SET operation is stored here.
